{"tid":2360035,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"iPad mini 螢幕加大至 8.4 吋或在 3 月登場","createTime":"2021-01-09T11:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T05:10:05.000Z","uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e51c09909579ff30f62b4faa77286ec05e2f50a0","tid":2360035,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T11:21:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2021/01/09/ipad-mini-2021-8-4-inch/?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2021%2F01%2F09%2Fipad-mini-2021-8-4-inch%2F%3F&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDVI2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=864a421e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2021/01/09/ipad-mini-2021-8-4-inch/?</a><br />\n<br />\n早在 2020 年已有消息指 iPad Mini 螢幕會變大，來自 Mac Otakara 的報導，他們從中國的蘋果供應鏈得到一些消息，即將要在今年推出的 iPad mini 2021（第 6 代 iPad mini），螢幕會由現時 7.9 吋增大至 8.4 吋，為了不讓機身變得太大，iPad mini 會改用更幼的邊框，預計會跟 iPad Air 3 相約。同時預計會像現時入門版 iPad 也將會改用幼邊框。<br />\n<br />\n至於會否使用 iPad Air 3 的電源鍵當作 Touch ID，消息指預期 iPad mini 仍會保留 Home Button 的 Touch ID 設計。而 iPad mini 2021 推出時間預計會在 2021 年 3 月份。<br />\n<br />\n而著名 Apple 分析員郭明錤曾在 2020 年 5 月發表報告，預計 iPad mini 將可能「變大」﹐由現時 7.9 吋提升至 8.5 吋至 9 吋之間，而今次的消息則是 8.4 吋，相距不太大。"},{"pid":"ae571906111a9630331e8a9846e0a8660a98abe4","tid":2360035,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T11:22:32.000Z","msg":"Android 化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b57c81b37c277a6f0d3755356ec5f197e0a832d9","tid":2360035,"uid":27416,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T11:23:43.000Z","msg":"仲用緊mini4<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b1aba2ff39ebefc1de4415b49a85c3f1407767","tid":2360035,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T11:25:13.000Z","msg":"仲算唔算mini<img src=\"/ass